tableau runs 

run mongo
run apache drill on top -> should be able to run a SQL query
tableau is a visualizer -> odbc driver


Audience:
 - Someone who knows how to use tableau


 Steps:
 1) Gather JSON data to insert into MongoDB for testing:
 	https://www.mockaroo.com/

 Other Notes:
 - http://www.tableau.com/about/blog/2015/6/tableau-mongodb-visual-analytics-json-speed-thought-39557
 	- tableau is now working with mongoDB, but only in BETA (as of june 2015). For MongoDB enterprise and tableau customers only. 


	------ Omitting installing of MongoDB -------------

	2) Adding data into Database
		- mongod --dbpath //Users/douglasfranklin/Documents/Dremio/data/db
		- use people
	 	- mongoimport --host 0.0.0.0:27017 --db people --collection MockCards < /Users/douglasfranklin/Documents/Dremio/MOCK_DATA_Cards.json
	 	- Make sure DB is working:
	 		- db.MockPeople.find({"last_name": "Webb"}) | Returns:
		 		{ "_id" : ObjectId("55f5c24e633034ea5bc2566f"), "id" : 7, "first_name" : "George", "last_name" : "Webb", "email" : "gwebb6@ted.com", "country" : "China" }
				{ "_id" : ObjectId("55f5c24e633034ea5bc25679"), "id" : 14, "first_name" : "Irene", "last_name" : "Webb", "email" : "iwebbd@goodreads.com", "country" : 			"France" }
				{ "_id" : ObjectId("55f5c24e633034ea5bc256c8"), "id" : 99, "first_name" : "Christina", "last_name" : "Webb", "email" : "cwebb2q@dailymotion.com", 			"country" : "Belarus" }
	3) Install drill
		- https://drill.apache.org/docs/installing-drill-on-linux-and-mac-os-x/
		- Need java for OSX
			- http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html
	4) MongoDB Plugin for Apache Drill
		- Navigate to "http://<IP address or host name>:8047/"
			- http://localhost:8047/
		- https://drill.apache.org/docs/mongodb-plugin-for-apache-drill/
	5) In the command line shell.
		- http://drill.apache.org/docs/mongodb-plugin-for-apache-drill/ to test everything. 
		- Navigate to /Users/douglasfranklin/Documents/Dremio/apache-drill-1.1.0
		- bin/drill-embedded to spin up instance
		- USE mongo.people
		- SHOW TABLES
		- SELECT * FROM MockPeople WHERE country = 'China';
			Returns:
