	6) Shell instance of Apache Drill is now working, now to test the relational properties we need to upload more data. 
		- Return to https://www.mockaroo.com/ to get more data. 
		- See image for more info, but create card data (money value for card balance, and card number of an ID)
		- Add this JSON data the mongo database the same way as before
		- Test out the relational properties!

			SELECT p.first_name FROM MockPeople p JOIN MockCards c ON p.id = c.id  WHERE c.cardBalance > 350;

